_sText:
This is a map made for the Dangerous Cargo Contest.

Terrorist try to protect their country by blowing up the dangerous missiles.

NOTE: It could be some people have some problems with the cubemaps (white glow). I never had this problem. But if you have open your console and type "buildcubemaps" and restart your game.

I had to hurry for this map so sorry if there are some problems.
